114
00:11:27,900 --> 00:11:30,140
Can you save him?

115
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:37,860
Before saving him, he must stand on the Minjing platform for us to investigate the cause of his injuries

116
00:11:37,860 --> 00:11:42,450
