117
00:11:42,450 --> 00:11:45,390
But he is weak.

118
00:11:45,390 --> 00:11:48,750
He's half dead.

119
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:52,300
If the brain is forced to open now...

120
00:11:58,020 --> 00:12:02,720
Elder, we can't see someone dying and not save him, right?

121
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:06,240
Elder, saving a person is important.

122
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:24,680
He's so seriously injured. It's better to deliver him to the Bodhi tree.

123
00:13:41,560 --> 00:13:43,360
You're awake?

124
00:13:48,180 --> 00:13:50,220
Did you all save me?

125
00:13:50,220 --> 00:13:51,930
Jingxuan!

126
00:13:53,490 --> 00:13:55,330
Come.

127
00:13:55,330 --> 00:13:56,890
Elder.

128
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:01,710
This person is the Elder of our Mingjing Village.

129
00:14:01,710 --> 00:14:04,380
He saved your life.

130
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:15,250
I don't know how to thank your kindness for saving my life.

131
00:14:15,250 --> 00:14:21,710
You don't need to thank me. I just hope you can answer me truthfully.

132
00:14:21,710 --> 00:14:23,400
Definitely.

133
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:29,150
Who are you? Why were you injured? Is there an enemy who wants to kill you?

134
00:14:29,150 --> 00:14:33,630
I'm Nan Yu Fu, main general of Spirit Armor Army.

135
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:38,700
I heard outsiders say it's the army of the governmental mansion?

136
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:44,280
Under the jurisdiction of Ghostdom, I led an army to attack the bandits.

137
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:48,510
Because I recklessly entered the enemy camp alone, I nearly lost my life.

138
00:14:48,510 --> 00:14:52,890
After I was seriously injured, the Yulin people

139
00:14:52,890 --> 00:14:57,190
told me as long as I enter Mingjing Village, I'll have some hope.

140
00:14:57,190 --> 00:15:01,680
No outsiders can know what Mingjing Village is like.

141
00:15:01,680 --> 00:15:05,420
I heard after a seriously injured person enters Mingjing Village

142
00:15:05,420 --> 00:15:10,700
