143
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:16,220
That's because before he is treated, his memory must be removed first.

144
00:15:16,220 --> 00:15:21,560
Your life was in danger, so you were an exception.

145
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:25,060
I hope to repay your kindness later for saving my life.

146
00:15:25,060 --> 00:15:29,250
We don't need repayment. It's just the ancestor's teachings here,

147
00:15:29,250 --> 00:15:33,610
